snippet.title: Moonstone Island | Romance Trailer | Fall in Love with Moonstone Island
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1658150/Moonstone_Island/ 

Meet the Romanceable Villagers in Moonstone Island! After a hard days travelling to over 100 islands in the sky, make a cozy date with one of your island's inhabitants and get to know the villagers! Chat, Joke, and Flirt your way to your match when Moonstone Island comes out later this year ♥ 

Moonstone Island is coming to PC and Nintendo Switch!
